creator: Mouwasat Developer
descriptionHtml:

يتيح تطبيق المواساة للهواتف الذكية لكم الحصول على مجموعة واسعة من الخدمات الإلكترونية الفريدة والتي نهدف من خلالها الى جعل تجربتكم أسرع وفي منتهى السهولة.

حجز المواعيد، استعراض المواعيد القادمة والسابقة، الأدوية الحالية والسابقة، النتائج الطبية، الموافقات الطبية، الفواتير، ربط أفراد العائلة


We are committed to providing the best medical services in all major and sub-specialties through distinguished qualified medical cadres from the most prestigious local and international universities using the latest technology in the field of medical equipment to achieve the best level of quality and safety for patients.

The Mouwasat application for smartphones allows you to access a wide range of unique electronic services, through which we aim to make your experience faster and easier.

حجز المواعيد، استعراض المواعيد القادمة والسابقة، الأدوية الحالية والسابقة، النتائج الطبية، الموافقات الطبية، الفواتير، ربط أفراد العائلة


We are committed to providing the best medical services in all major and sub-specialties through distinguished qualified medical cadres from the most prestigious local and international universities using the latest technology in the field of medical equipment to achieve the best level of quality and safety for patients.

The Mouwasat application for smartphones allows you to access a wide range of unique electronic services, through which we aim to make your experience faster and easier. Integrated with Health Connect to seamlessly access and track your health data. This allows us to present your information in an intuitive and visually appealing way while enabling our doctors to provide you with more accurate and personalized assessments.

Appointment Scheduling, Appointments Histories, Medications, Medical Approvals, Invoices, Sick leaves, Dependents
